flowchart TD
  A[Browse Catalog] --> B[Add Items to Cart]
  B --> C[Review Cart]
  C -->|Update/Remove| C
  C --> D[Checkout]
  D --> E[Create Order from Cart]
  E --> F[Process Payment]
  F -->|Approved| G[Confirm Order]
  F -->|Declined| H[Prompt Retry/Cancel]
  G --> I[Fulfillment Service]
  I --> J[Prepare Shipment]
  J --> K[Mark Fulfilled + Notify User]